DynamicIndicators.formula: ( "Elec_Grid.Total Cost Function" + "Wind_farm.Total Cost Function" ) / ( "Elec_Grid.Levelized Grid extraction ElectricalEnergy GridFlow" + "Wind_farm.Levelized ImposedProfile ElectricalEnergy SourceLoadFlow" + "Elec_Grid_Inject.Levelized Grid injection ElectricalEnergy GridFlow" )
DynamicIndicators.name: Elec_cost

DynamicIndicators.formula: ("ELY_PEM.Total Cost Function" - "ELY_PEM.CONS Levelized Total ElectricalEnergy UsedPower" * "Elec_cost" + "H2_Tank.Total Cost Function" )/ "ELY_PEM.PROD Levelized Total FluidH2Mass H2MassFlowRate"
DynamicIndicators.name: LCOH
